spanGrp.span: Yís të sũã'-ra jeska jirö jirö desãu (_)
a white car was going on a trail;
tebeli_yaga surrunã (m) je damãu-lo klá wöke-lë pe-wa inga
and then I see there are many things there;
keanẽ jeska nẽ jirö tsõ tã'ĩ yís sũẽ rö
there was something to eat and a red monkey made noise with it in the hole of a tree.
Jirö kata-nã bi tsõ jo je wa pablar-gẽ kal wöjenẽi nã (m)
Keanẽ nã jere jeska pe tsõ pe jũ tsõ pe jirö tsõ pe deli tsõ
people were playing; a child was playing with something to kick.
pe jinõ-gẽ (_) peyaba jinõ-gẽ jinõ-glö shtö wa tenã' shtö
All that can be seen there; there was all that.
Je klabe juer-gẽ jeska je klabe tsõ jeska
There are nice things, like vehicles to fly, things to eat,
Je í rö/ jirö tsõ bá juela pe tebeli_yaga (_) jirö se junã-glö bi damãu-lo jirö se wã (m) kata-nã bi je köũ
but they were in bad condition.
I saw that the place was nice, just like we are here.
Je klabe yís sũã'-ra kã' rö bá jeska/ jiska se kajali bi
We have nothing; there are many things that are not OK; that’s how I see it.
Ka se je wã jirö ta Je rö jeska ra jirö köũ ka rö böi ta kuna Jebi yís sũẽ rö
That’s it, but we don’t get that far.
Jebi í rö Taranã (extra) ka se je ka se je dö-mĩ jega
Until then I saw that everything was OK.
Tara jeska bö yís sũã'-ra jebi köũ (_) bá ramã
There were things; there was a man with a mustache with his forehead wrapped up.
Jebi jirö (_) tsõ pekaga kajki kalgu ta kalgu ta jirö (_) jirö wöchichei pajie-lë bi
I saw that everything was like that; the place looked all blue.
Jebi klabe í kajki (_) yís sũã'-ra jebi jeme ra kã' bi jirö bi (_) juela siú rama köũmĩ siú rama köũmĩ
We don’t have something like that here.
Ka (m) je kõnã se je ĩã mãĩ jiska jebi
I saw that the place was nice.
Jebi yís sũã'-ra kã' rö böi
Ka rö ka rö sulwi kuna
We don’t have something like that;
ka lë se je wã jirö ta je kepi
but in that place there was that.
